Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（澤圭(たくけい)たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（澤圭たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.52,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:35.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 兄貴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）\Nすげえぞ お前ら！ よくやった！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.24,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,That was incredible, guys. Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:48.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原(すうげん)）ああ　だが もう十分だ\N（去亥(きょがい)）そういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.24,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.41,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）クッ… 飛信(ひしん)隊 退却だー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.91,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Feixin Unit, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）オーッ！\N（兵士）飛信隊 退却だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.93,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Feixin Unit, retreat! Feixin Unit, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊 退却だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（万極(まんごく)）うん？ 飛信隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.92,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,Fei...xin... Unit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:04.93,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,The ones who killed Feng Ji... The Feixin Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが馮忌(ふうき)を討った飛信隊か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）その後\N秦第４軍と趙(ちょう)万極軍の戦いは―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.81,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After that, the battle between the Fourth Qin Army and the Zhao Wan Ji Army
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:13.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙軍優勢の一方的な展開となった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.98,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,developed into the Zhao army having an overwhelming advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一騎打ちの末\N万極が 第４軍軍長 干央(かんおう)に―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:21.78,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The reason for it was when Wan Ji dealt with the Fourth Army Combat Commander, Gan Yang during a one-on-one fight on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:21.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,深手を負わせたことが\Nきっかけであった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:26.66,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,During that fight, Pang Nuan stood still for a little while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その争いの中 龐煖は\Nしばらく たたずんでいたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.33,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,he eventually disappeared back into the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）再び 闇の中へ姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊は犠牲を出しながらも\N混戦の中心部より脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:39.26,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Although they suffered casualties, the Feixin Unit was able to escape the center of the melee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.51,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and somehow they made it to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとか山中まで逃れた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それに対し―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:50.52,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But Wan Ji personally led a suppression unit on a large-scale pursuit for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:50.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万極は自ら討伐隊を率いて\N大規模な追撃を行った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（副官）包囲を広げる！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Spread an encirclement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隙間は歩兵で埋めよ！\N１人も逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fill gaps with foot soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let a single one of them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N山々に響き渡る騎馬の轟音(ごうおん)と―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:05:00.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The roars of numerous horse hooves and throngs of wriggling torches that spread throughout the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:03.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うごめくタイマツの火の数が\N追撃のすさまじさを物語っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,told of the ferocity of the pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何人やられた？\N（崇原）分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.07,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,How many were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.07,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの伍(ご)は無事だが…\N竜川(りゅうせん) お前のとこは？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.74,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,My Wu is all right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.16,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,Long Chuan, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜川）ううん…\N（松左(しょうさ)）俺んとこも３人やられた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.66,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Three of ours were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜有(りゅうゆう)たちがいねえな\N（崇原）山に入る前に はぐれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.35,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Long You and his group aren't here, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.00,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,They split off before we got into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中鉄(ちゅうてつ)と魯延(ろえん)どの\Nそれに山民族の連中もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.66,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,Zhong Tie and Lord Lu Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.42,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,The Mountain Folk group, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（澤圭）羌瘣君は？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.25,Kingdom-Main,Ze,0,0,0,,What about Young Qiang Lei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原）\N田有(でんゆう)が抱きかかえるところは見たが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.18,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,I saw Tian You pick him up, but after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから先は…\N（澤圭）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても\Nもうちょっとだったのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.21,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,But anyhow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.89,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Man, we were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 惜しかった\N（沛浪）もう少しで大将首か…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.31,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Yes. It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.84,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Just a little more and we could've taken the Great General's head...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取ったら取ったで\N大変だったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.31,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,If we had taken it, though, it would've really been something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村の英雄どころか\N国の英雄になるところだった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.81,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Forget heroes of our village, we'd be heroes of the whole state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:43.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）\Nハハハッ！ そりゃ確かに大事(おおごと)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.81,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,It sure would've been huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:48.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし つくづく大した男だぜ\Nうちらの大将は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:48.57,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,But you know, our general really is quite a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ\N（崇原）間違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.08,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,Yeah. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.49,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,A bit of an idiot though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アホだけどな\N（竜川）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）\N尾到！ そのガキ 絶対に離すなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wei Dao, no matter what happens, don't let go of that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち雑魚が どれだけ死のうが\Nそいつさえ生きてりゃ―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Cause no matter how many of us small fries die,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,as long as that guy survives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊は死なねえんだからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.41,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,the Feixin Unit will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）\Nなんで お前らが泣くんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.72,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Why're you guys dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Because we're... from the same hometown as Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昴(こう)）だって 僕ら 信の同郷だから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶(けい)）\N伍長たちが みんな 信のことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All of the Wuchang seeing that Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らの信が こんなにまでなれて\N泣かずにいられねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:19.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Seeing Xin reach this far... How could we not cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ 尾平？\N（尾平）ああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Right, Wei Ping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.02,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.98,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,What're you talking about, Qing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:24.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）何言ってんだよ 慶さん\N信は まだまだ これから…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.98,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Xin's only just getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ… もう来たか\Nウワサどおり速(はえ)えな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're as fast as the rumors say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（松左）どっからだ？\N音が響いて分からねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.71,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Where're they coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.60,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,With all the echoing, I can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）矢だ！ 伏せろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:40.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.72,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,They're coming! From the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るぞ！ 左だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたぞ 飛信隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.01,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,Found you, Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り囲め！ １人も逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.05,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Surround them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let one of them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… お前(めえ)ら\N（崇原･田永）うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.76,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.27,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Hey! Guy with the long white hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）おい！ そこの長髪白髪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえが隊長だな\Nいいのか？ こんな緩い包囲で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.24,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,You're the captain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.41,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,You think you're gonna be all right with such a loose encirclement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:25.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは 馮忌軍に風穴を開けて\N将を討ち取った飛信隊だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:25.36,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,We're the Feixin Unit that opened a hole in the Feng Ji army and took the general's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,甘く見てると\Nその首 たたき落とすぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.67,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,If you underestimate us, we'll lop that head of your right off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（万極）やってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.55,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:36.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で死ぬタマじゃねえぞ\Nこの飛信隊は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.73,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,This Feixin Unit ain't the type to die out in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.06,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Got that, you bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんな？ てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.56,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,What are Pei Lang and the others doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沛浪たち 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ…\N（沛浪）飛信隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.69,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）脱出だー！\N（騎兵）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.19,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.45,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.47,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Run down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）\N下へ走れ！ とにかく下へ走れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.38,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Run down there for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:57.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵１）追え！\N（騎兵２）逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（副官）フフッ… バカどもが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下に どれだけの兵が\N待ち構えていると思っているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do they have any idea how many soldiers we have stationed down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 俺たちを逃がすために…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.53,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,To let us get away, they all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちじゃねえ… 信をだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.47,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.06,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ 到！\N（尾到）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:17.97,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.56,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.31,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Did you come all the way out here in the middle of the night for Wei Ping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里(ゆうり)）こんな真夜中に\N尾平のために お祈りかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:40.16,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Aren't you the same way, Miss You Li? For Wei Dao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（東美(とうび)）そういう友里さんだって\N尾到君のために…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）私は ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.89,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）尾到に尾平\Nバカ兄弟を頼んだぞっと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:50.52,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Wei Dao and Wei Ping, I'm counting on you two idiot brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと 友里さん\N守り石さまに！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.76,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Wait, Miss You Li! Tapping the guardian stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）帰ろっか\N（東美）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.08,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Wanna head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:01.58,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 東美？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:07.90,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Dong Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 怖いよ 友里さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.22,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Miss You Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:18.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は もう… 尾平さんたち\N死んでしまってるんじゃないかって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:17.91,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,I keep thinking... that Wei Ping and the others might really die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（泣き声）\N東美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.32,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Dong Mei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.73,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,You idiot. What are they going to do if the ones back here waiting for them don't even believe in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってる あんたが\N信じてやんなくて どうすんのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾平のヤツが かわいそうだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.03,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Wei Ping and those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.41,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（東美）だって… だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:39.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）大丈夫！ あの兄弟は\N運だけは 人一倍 強いから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.59,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:39.08,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Those brothers have better luck than the average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.42,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,When push comes to shove, that guy always manage to make it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと いざってときは\Nなんとかしてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.06,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里典(りてん)の所にいた信君？\N（友里）そう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.96,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Xin? The one who worked at Li Dian's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.19,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.75,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Remember what Wei Ping said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾到が言ってたよ\N“あいつはバカだけど―”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.20,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,He's an idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“そこらの武将より\N頼りになる”って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.28,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,but he's more reliable than just any military commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:59.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（友里）最近よく同じ夢を見るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:00.07,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,I've been having the same dream a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.60,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,A dream of the two of them coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人が帰ってくる夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちの気苦労なんて\Nこれっぽっちも分かってなくてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.79,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,They don't have the faintest idea of how worried we are about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.60,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Wei Dao laughs like a horse when he sees my face while saying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:10.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾到のヤツ 私の顔見たら\N高笑いして言うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“大将首 取ったぞ！”って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.84,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,"I took the head of a Great General!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:17.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホント？ 尾到君 ホントに\N大将の首なんて取ってきちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.55,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.84,Kingdom-Main,Dong,0,0,0,,Wei Dao is really gonna take the head of a Great General?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ いや それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.20,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I dunno about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:25.81,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,But, knowing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あいつのことだから―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:31.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと 頑張ってさ\Nすごい手柄を上げてると思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.66,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.89,Kingdom-Main,You,0,0,0,,I'll bet he'll render some incredible achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.62,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴…\N（尾平）あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.95,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.02,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Sorry. Just go on a head for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い ちょっと先に行っててくれ\N俺は少し休んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.63,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぁに すぐに追いつくから…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.47,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, I'll catch up in a minute, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 到 お前 その矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.03,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Dao... That arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 頑張ろう 兄貴\Nいつもの信みたいに―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.85,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Let's hang in there, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:02.85,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Just like Xin always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.25,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Let's grit our teeth and move our feet forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歯ぁ食いしばって\N足を前に進めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵１）血痕を見つけたぞ\N万極さまをお呼びしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We found a blood trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Call Lord Wan Ji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There are two pairs of tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵２）\N足跡は２つ　くぼみの深さから―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,From the depth of the depressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人は もう１人\N担いでいるかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,one of them may be carrying another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:28.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よって ２人ないし３人が\N山を登って逃走しています
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:28.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So two, no, three people are climbing the mountain to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだ 間違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.50,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,That's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.00,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵２）\Nしかし ひとつだけ解(げ)せぬことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:35.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But there is one thing I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵２）この出血の量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The amount of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっくに死んでいても\Nおかしくありません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It would not be odd to have died a while ago after losing this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして動けるのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,How can they still be moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アッ…\N（尾到）兄貴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:46.81,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まだ終わらねえ\N終わってたまる…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.72,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I-I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.56,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Like hell it's gonna end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:55.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）兄貴 すまねえ\Nそこまでの傷とは知らずに…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.74,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.79,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't know how hurt you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）うるせえよ バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.86,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Shut up, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえの傷だって\Nひでえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.63,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,You've got a pretty awful wound yourself, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）追っ手が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.10,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Pursuers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:08.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 無理かもしれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.33,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,We might not have a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:14.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）到\N信のヤツ 心の臓は動いてっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:14.72,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Dao. Is Xin's heart still beating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ちゃんと動いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.25,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's beating like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.63,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Both you and I can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\N俺のも お前のも まだ動いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら\Nいつもの信は こう言うよな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:24.22,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,So if Xin were awake, he'd say something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“まだ何も終わってねえ”ってよ\N（尾到）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.72,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,"Nothings over with yet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢は骨で止まってんだよな？ 到\N（尾到）ああ まだいける
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.52,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,That arrow's stopped at your bone, isn't it, Dao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.23,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし…\Nじゃ 俺たち ここで別れるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.48,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Okay. Then we'll split up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:44.59,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,They're bound to be following the trail of our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）ヤツらは―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺らの血をたどってきてんだろう\N（服を破る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前は\Nこれで血を止めて登っていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.49,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,So you've gotta use this to stop the bleeding and climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど…\N（尾平）到！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:47.99,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:49.99,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちで信を守り抜くんだ\N飛信隊の伍長として！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.71,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,We're going to protect Xin through to the end of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.87,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,As Wuchang of the Feixin Unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城戸村(じょうとむら)のダチとしてな\N（尾到）兄貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.00,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,and as friends from Chenghu Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.22,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（たたく音）\Nフッ… 妙な顔すんな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.86,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Don't start making weird faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらをまいたら\Nお前のあとを追って また合流する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:11.22,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,After I've shaken those guys off, I'll come catch back up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.27,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I'm not planning on dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ気はねえぞ\N村で東美が待ってるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.52,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Dong Mei is waiting for me at the village after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信を頼んだぞ 到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.53,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Take care of Xin, Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.63,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:48.43,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Th-These arrows... They didn't stop at the bone, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この矢 骨で止まってなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ… お互い満身創痍だな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.77,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,We're both pretty covered in wounds, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが くたばりゃしねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.44,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But we aren't gonna drop dead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城戸村の男は頑丈が売りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.74,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,The selling point of us men of Chenghu Village is our sturdiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ？ 信… そうだろう？ 兄貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.27,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Ain't that right, Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.52,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,We are, right, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）ほう… てめえらか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.72,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下僕のくせして 大将軍とか\Nアホなこと ほざいてるガキは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:15.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,The brats spouting about being Great Generals or whatever even though they're just servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nああ？ 大体 この尾兄弟に挨拶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.55,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,You should at least greet us Wei Brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（殴る音）\N（尾到）あ… 兄貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.40,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.51,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Dao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）何やってる 到！\Nこのガキ ぶっ殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,Kill these brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ヘヘヘッ… バ～カ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.52,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.47,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,Dao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）到！\N（信）思い知ったか チンピラども
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,Get it, hoodlums?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:34.00,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,Don't look down on the greatest generals under the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天下の大将軍をナメんじゃねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（漂(ひょう)）おい 行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Piao,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.73,Kingdom-Flashback,Ping,0,0,0,,D-Dammit! We'll remember this, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nくそ… 覚えてろよ てめえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,Those are the ones we've been hearing rumors about lately, Xin and Piao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）\Nあれが最近ウワサの信と漂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）気がついたか 信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.51,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Awake, Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）おお… 尾到か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wei Dao...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 なんか\N村にいたころの夢を見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:59.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I just had a dream about when we were back at the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）偶然だな　俺もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.38,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,What a coincidence. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 龐煖！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッ！\N（尾到）まだ動かないほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.52,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,You shouldn't start moving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,横んなってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.57,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:20.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どうなってんだ？ 尾到\Nここは どこだ？ 戦いは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on, Wei Dao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Where are we? What happened to the battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:28.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Everyone put themselves in danger so I could get away, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:28.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を逃がすために\Nみんなが体張ったってのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！ 何やってんだ 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shit! What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 干央は どうなった？\Nいや 龐煖は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What about Gan Yang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No, where's Pang Nuan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウウッ…\N（尾到）信 その話 やめにしねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.71,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.12,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,How about we stop talking about those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:44.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの顔を思い出すだけで\N治る傷も治らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:44.24,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Just remembering that guy's face won't heal your wounds faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… お前 ケガしてんのか？\Nちょっと見せてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let me see for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）\N大丈夫だ　お前ほど重傷じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.05,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,It's okay. They're not as bad as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 今は ほんの少しだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:58.01,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But just for a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しい話がしたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.06,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.10,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Xin, do you remember
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信 覚えてるか？\Nお前は“大将軍になる”つってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.35,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,when you said you'd become a "Great General"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:11.32,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,and we said "No you won't" and we all made fun of you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“なれっこねえ”って\N俺たちは みんな バカにしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ！ だから 毎回\Nぶっ飛ばしてやっただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So I'd beat the crap outta you guys on a daily basis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.08,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Become a Great General, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“大将軍になる”か…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 戦場に出て感じたよ\N正に“夢”だってな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.61,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I've felt it ever since I set foot on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.39,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,It truly is a "dream".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.72,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Just how much do you need to fight to make it that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ戦えば たどりつくんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつでも しくじれば\Nそこで死んで 全部 終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:32.17,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,If you just fail once and die there, it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:35.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）楽しい話しするんじゃ\Nなかったのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Weren't we gonna talk about something fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.10,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）してんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:41.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 龐煖相手に生き残った\N（信）それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.91,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,You survived a fight with Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.89,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Yeah. It wasn't just your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）\Nそうだ お前だけの力じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊のみんなが命を懸けて\Nお前を守ったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:50.54,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Everyone in the unit risked their lives to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.60,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Even without an order, we risked out lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命令でもないのに 命懸けで…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.95,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,That's not something that happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは普通のことじゃねえ\N普通の隊長には できねえよ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.05,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,That's something normal captains can't do, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 思ったんだ\N“信は本当に将軍になれる”ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.53,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,So I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.33,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,you really can become a general, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.36,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Like the famous Great Generals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名だたる大将軍たち…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎でさえ きっと こうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.44,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Even that Wang Qi must've been like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人じゃ\Nどうしようもねえときもあった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.64,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,They've had times when they were hopeless on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう思うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.32,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（せきこみ）\N（信）お… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 仲間の力込みで\Nお前の力だ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.02,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But the power of your comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.36,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,is also part of your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:33.94,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Xin, I was truly glad to have been your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は\Nお前の友達で本当に良かったと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Wei Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待てよ 尾到\Nお前 何言ってんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:38.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ… お前と一緒にいると―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:44.33,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,When I was with you, my heart was always beating out of my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっとワクワクしっぱなしだった\N（信）尾到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wei Dao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.90,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Tonight, quite a few comrades may have died
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）今夜 結構な仲間が\N死んだかもしんねえが―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下向く必要はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.23,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,but there's no need to look downwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦争やってんだ 死人は出るさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.95,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,We're fighting a war. There will be deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだよ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.67,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,It's all right, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.22,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I think everyone wants to dream with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな お前と一緒に\N夢を見てえと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.61,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからも お前は そうやって―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.98,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,By continuing to do that into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.40,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,you'll ride on the emotions of a crowd of comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大勢の仲間の思いを乗せて―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.48,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,and rise up to become the greatest general under the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天下の大将軍に駆け上がるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾到… お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wei Dao. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対なれるぞ 信…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:22.45,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I'm certain you'll... become it... Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…なんつってな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.38,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）バ… バカ野郎 てめえ！\Nふざけんじゃねえよ くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Y-You goddamn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't joke around about something like that, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到）ハハッ… すまん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.99,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…\Nガラにもなく 長く しゃべった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.88,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,It's weird for me to talk for this long...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し眠ろう 信\Nそれで力取り戻したら―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.67,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But let's rest a little, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:48.58,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,When I get my strength back, I'm gonna bring you to meet everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が\Nみんなの所に連れてってやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントに大丈夫か？ 尾到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Are you really okay, Wei Dao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 寝れば治る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.23,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be okay if I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.55,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,You Li...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんなよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit... screwing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度も同じ手 食うかよ… 尾到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You think I'll fall for the same thing twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wei Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… しつけえぞ　早く起きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,G-Give it up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hurry and wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起きろよ 尾到！\Nこ… こんなのあるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wake up, Wei Dao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎… バカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:52.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You idiot... You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）石笛の音… あっちか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The sound of the flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:03.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）なに？\Nそれじゃ 尾兄弟たった２人に―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You're saying you left Xin to just the two Wei brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信を託したってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうするしかなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.79,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,That was our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに\Nあいつらなら大丈夫だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.84,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,And I thought he'd be okay if he was with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You really thought that would be safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）マジで大丈夫かよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's Wuchang Wei Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N尾平伍長だ 尾平伍長が戻ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.77,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wuchang Wei Ping is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）\Nで… 田有　一体 どうして尾平と…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.87,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,T-Tian You, why the hell are you with Wei Ping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）ちょっと待て！\N信と尾到がいねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Xin and Wei Dao aren't with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有）追っ手をかわすために\N尾平が囮(おとり)になったらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.37,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Apparently Wei Ping acted as a decoy so they could escape some pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちも\Nさっき こいつと合流したばっかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We only just met back up with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信を守ってるのは尾到だけか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So only Wei Dao is protecting Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）到なら大丈夫だ\N（去亥たち）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.13,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,If he's with Dao... he'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつはマジで頼りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:42.18,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He's seriously reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ きっと… 矢傷で動けないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.63,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,But with his arrow wounds, he won't be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:48.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたねえ 捜索隊を出すぞ！\N（田永）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.89,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.65,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Let's send out a search party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひとっ走りだ！\Nケガ人は ここにいろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,One more run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:50.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wounded men, stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:51.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（石(せき)）\Nその必要はない　隊長は帰還された
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.09,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The captain has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:57.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）なに？\N（ざわめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:54.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）信だ！\N（兵士）信が戻ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Xin came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく戻ったな 信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.12,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Good job getting back, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾平 すまねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:11.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ping. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶･昴）尾到…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.48,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Wei Dao...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.02,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Mr Wei Dao...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nフッ… なんで お前が謝るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.80,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らも泣くな 慶 昴\N泣くこたぁねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.81,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,And stop crying, Qing, Ang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:36.00,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,There's nothing to cry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは やり遂げた\N立派に役目をやり遂げたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.27,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,This guy did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:41.32,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He brilliantly fulfilled his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 涙は要らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.42,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,So there's no need for any tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういうときは\N笑って褒めてやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:47.78,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,At times like this, you smile... and praise people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:52.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほ… 本当に よく頑張ったなって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.25,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Y... You really did a great job...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:01.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,到ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:03.05,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Dao!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:12.60,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,You did well not to die after taking that attack from Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖の あの一撃を食らって\Nよく死ななかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは 一体 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:16.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What the hell is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの強さ 今でも信じられねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:19.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That strength... I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.61,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,That man was a certain type of "seeker".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は ある種の求道者(ぐどうしゃ)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:24.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Seeker?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,求道者？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:30.75,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,One who leaves populated villages and focuses solely on finding a "path".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）人里離れ\Nひたすら 道を求め 極めんとする者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:36.28,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,He is one who sought only strength and built himself up through training that we cannot even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強さのみを求め―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:36.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の想像の及ばぬほどの修練を\N積み重ねた者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな修練だよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What kind of training?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見当もつかない\Nだが こちらも修練を重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.18,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I couldn't even guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:44.88,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,But we must train as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,半年後には 私が勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.63,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,In half a year, I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:51.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）半年もねえよ 羌瘣\Nこの戦でヤツを討つんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:50.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It won't be in half a year, Qiang Lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:51.85,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We'll beat him in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Because he is the enemy Great General, we have to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツが敵の大将である以上\N討たなきゃなんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:01.94,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Wei Dao... He was a good guy, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:02.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾到 いいヤツだったな\N（信）ああ
